        </p>
        <p>In the following exercises, solve each inequality, graph the solution, and write the solution in interval notation.</p>
      </introduction>
      <exercise xml:id="PREALG-Xolup1CF10-parts" original="PREALG/modules/m81367/index.cnxml" license="CC-BY-4.0">
        <statement>
          <ol marker="(a)" cols="2">
            <li>
              <m>x &lt; 3</m> and <m>x \ge 1</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>x \le 4</m> and <m>x &gt; −2</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>x \ge −4</m> and <m>x \le −1</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>x &gt; −6</m> and <m>x &lt; −3</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>5x-2 &lt; 8</m> and <m>6x+9 \ge 3</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>4x-1 &lt; 7</m> and <m>2x+8 \ge 4</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>4x+6 \le 2</m> and<m>2x+1 \ge −5</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>4x-2 \le 4</m> and<m>7x-1 &gt; −8</m>
            </li>
            <li>
              <m>2x-11 &lt; 5</m> and<m>3x-8 &gt; −5</m>
            </li>
