    <exercisegroup>
      <introduction>
        <p>
          <em>Solve Compound Inequalities with “or”</em>
        </p>
        <p>In the following exercises, solve each inequality, graph the solution on the number line, and write the solution in interval notation.</p>
      </introduction>
      <exercise xml:id="PREALG-7FftY2CxnI-parts" original="PREALG/modules/m81367/index.cnxml" license="CC-BY-4.0">
        <statement>
          <ol marker="(a)" cols="2">
            <li>
              <m>x \le −2</m> or <m>x &gt; 3</m>
            </li>
